###< symfony/asset-mapper ###

# Runtime upload directory — company logos etc. are user data, not code.
# Pattern with /* + re-include of .gitkeep so git honors the negation
# (a trailing-slash ignore on the parent folder would block re-includes
# inside it).
/public/uploads/*
!/public/uploads/.gitkeep

# Local Claude Code context (not shared in repo)
/CLAUDE.md
/.claude/

# Git workflow skill state (local tooling, not source)
/.git-workflow/

